{"id":232976719,"title":"臺灣人的瘋狂","content":"最近看到了一篇中國留學生質疑台灣某間大學行政的文，內文如下：\n\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/6d3d1278-9249-42e2-8977-2b5fac4a423f/1280.jpeg\n\n\n接下來馬上就得到臺灣網友熱情的回應\n\n\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/819579c1-a8dc-4129-892e-f42fdfd784b1/1280.jpeg\n\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/6e012440-2345-4a8b-923b-eb3dc9596061/1280.jpeg\n\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/5081db86-4025-40da-9eba-7ebfd3defac6/1280.jpeg\n\n\n基本上發文者只是在質疑學校為什麼不管是否來自湖北都要關在同一棟，沒有分級管理。這樣就引來了臺灣大批網民的撻伐。甚至還有很多人去他的個版看到可以留言的地方就去留言罵他...\n這篇文上他並沒有在批評臺灣，只是在質疑學校的行政命令。如果一個來自非中國的外國學生發文質疑學校的行政，會被網友一面倒的說滾出臺灣嗎？","excerpt":"最近看到了一篇中國留學生質疑台灣某間大學行政的文，內文如下：接下來馬上就得到臺灣網友熱情的回應，基本上發文者只是在質疑學校為什麼不管是否來自湖北都要關在同一棟，沒有分級管理。這樣就引來了臺灣大批網民的","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"fc7574ad-e1df-43d2-bb06-8825c718c065","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-29T06:00:53.395Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-29T06:02:03.236Z","commentCount":28,"likeCount":20,"tags":[],"topics":["臺灣人","武漢肺炎","時事"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"時事","forumAlias":"trending","school":"國立中正大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":16},{"id":"514c2569-fd53-4d9d-a415-bf0f88e7329f","count":3},{"id":"aa0d425f-d530-4478-9a77-fe3aedc79eea","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/6d3d1278-9249-42e2-8977-2b5fac4a423f/1280.jpeg"},{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/819579c1-a8dc-4129-892e-f42fdfd784b1/1280.jpeg"},{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/6e012440-2345-4a8b-923b-eb3dc9596061/1280.jpeg"},{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/5081db86-4025-40da-9eba-7ebfd3defac6/1280.jpeg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"04ca2105-7696-4ad4-8b56-ce24